  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "<b>Scalability and Power</b>\r\nThe high-voltage battery system by Safran
    x Saft paves the way for a true revolution in onboard energy, thanks to packs
    connected in parallel reaching up to 800 VDC. These packs are configurable  to
    meet the power and energy requirements of the aircraft.\r\n\r\n<b>Modular Design</b>\r\nThe
    modules, adjustable in length to suit the requirements of each aircraft, are
    designed for seamless integration. Made from composite material with liquid cooling,
    they ensure advanced safety, adhering to the strict standards of the aerospace
    industry.\r\n\r\n<b>Innovative Cell Technology</b>\r\nThe LMFP-blend technology
    was selected as the first solution for its optimal balance between performance
    (280 Wh/kg, 2000 W/kg) and safety. Solid-state technology, targeting even higher
    performance levels (400 Wh/kg, 1600 W/kg) ) represents the next development stage.
    Pouch cell formats with opposing tabs are configurable from 15 Ah to 55 Ah, allowing
    battery sizing adjustments by varying only the cell thickness.\r\n\r\n\u2022
    Unmatched Scalability and Power\r\n\r\n\u2022 Modular design\r\n\r\n\u2022 Innovative
    Electrochemistry, \r\nfrom LMFP-blend to Solid-State"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0724974d955485f498e7e26769f2a200, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -7490216427898086963, guid: 0724974d955485f498e7e26769f2a200, type: 2}
